front.title: •A Day Long Remembered
front.gametext: If Obi-Wan not on table, deploy on Yavin 4 or Hoth system. If system 'Blown away,' relocate to opponent's side of table. Rebels and Rebel starships are deploy +8 and lost immunity to attrition. Canceled if Obi-Wan is deployed. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: 'It has seen the end of Kenobi and will soon see the end of the Rebellion.'
